Sybil Seely https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sybil_Seely 0 Sybil Seely (January 2, 1902 – June 26, 1984) was a silent film actress who worked with the well known silent film comedy actor Buster Keaton. She was credited in most of her films as Sibye Trevilla.
